'''El Mahdy Mohamed Soliman Ibrahim''' ({{langx|ar|المهدي محمد سليمان إبراهيم}}; born 8 June 1987) is an Egyptian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for the [[Egyptian Premier League]] side [[Zamalek SC]] and the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]].<ref>{{Cite web |last=El-Ramady |first=Ahmed |date=2022-07-31 |title=Ittihad of Alexandria confirm signing of El-Mahdy Soliman from Pyramids |url=https://www.kingfut.com/2022/07/31/ittihad-of-alexandria-el-mahdy-soliman/ |access-date=2023-04-28 |website=KingFut |language=en-GB}}</ref>

